results.occurrenceRemarks: I love this shot--it looks like the wind is so strong that it's blowing this gemsbok's horns sideways.  It's not uncommon to see a gemsbok without perfectly straight horns (particularly on game farms), but this one's horn deformity was fairly strong.  Location approximate to northern CKGR.
